title: Bug 116609[Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description:
Bug 116609: [Regression] Color orange doesn't work. 

Description: When trying to use the color orange in the application, it is not being displayed correctly.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the application.

OB: The color orange is not shown correctly in the application.
EB: The color orange should be displayed correctly in the application.
SR: 1. Open the application. Attempt to use the color orange in different parts of the application, such as text, background, or buttons. Verify if the color is displayed correctly.
